<h1>Save 100 million lives from cardiovascular disease</h1>

<p class="intro">18 million people die from cardiovascular disease each year. A majority of these premature deaths occurring in low- and middle-income countries. Proven, scalable solutions exist, but there has been little investment and little progress made so far.</p>

