<h2>How to save 100 million lives</h2>
<p>Resolve to Save Lives aims to save 100 million lives from cardiovascular disease by focusing on three evidence-based interventions.</p>

<ol>
<li>Increase coverage of hypertension treatment to 70%</li>
<li>Reduce sodium consumption by 30%</li>
<li>Eliminate trans fat from the global food supply</li>
</ol>

